com.camerontec.util.datamodel.fix

Class FIXBytesMessageTranslator<M extends Message>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.camerontec.util.datamodel.fix.FIXBytesMessageTranslator<M>
  • Type Parameters:
    M - the message type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    MessageTranslator<M,BytesSegmentBuffer>

    public class FIXBytesMessageTranslator<M extends Message>
extends Object
implements MessageTranslator<M,BytesSegmentBuffer>
    A message translator implementation which translates between canonical messages and any other message which can be represented as a byte array.

    Instances of this class may be configured with the following properties:

    • utcDateTimePattern (default: yyyyMMdd-HH:mm:ss): Specifies how to encode/decode fields of type UTC date/time.
    • importMessageStructure (default: true): Specifies whether to import fields into a nested structure on deserialization. If false then all fields are imported into the root group.
    • allowNoLengthOnRawData (default: false): Specifies whether to allow importation of raw data fields which are not preceded by a raw data length field.
